minimally damaging.

00:08:08.850 --> 00:08:12.570
And, in some cases,
we can enhance the performance of a

00:08:12.570 --> 00:08:16.280
material. So,
we are going to get tailored

00:08:16.280 --> 00:08:35.026
properties through defect
engineering.

